{
  "stem": "13673.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No-- there wasn't a country in the world that wanted him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother could have gone to England as a domestic, this woman who had never done a stitch of work in her life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because my father didn't have any manual skills, and she refused to leave him-- leave without him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So England was already out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, there were-- there was a cousin that emigrated to Argentina, but he was a refugee himself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Another-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, an-- an-- her brother escaped to Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm not sure if she knew-- at what point she knew that he was in Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was my mother's brother, another uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the uncle that lived next door to me got to America before my parents did and was-- and I have letters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have documents in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was astounded, though, when I read them just recently, how much work he put into getting them here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to have a guarantor, is it called?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he found this very distant relative who lived here, and he became the guarantor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they got a visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then the visa fell through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they got passage on a ship, finally, leaving from Portugal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a rather similar story to my husband's, who also left via Spain and Portugal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, my parents did too, only they had to take a train to Spain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were supposed to go on one ship, and then that ship-- somehow that didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That-- to make a long story short, the third ship was the-- finally the one that they were able to get onto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this was in July, 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
